metadata.name: Let's Breathe #1/100
metadata.description:
The feeling when your body softens and your mind becomes clear,  
The wind grazes your face, and your nostrils flare,  
The coolness of air circling the insides of your cheeks,  
The relief you feel from the anxiety of the past weeks.

This is "Lets Breathe"  
An artwork created out a haiku, as the haiku itself was created from the artwork. The art illustrates the necessity to take time to breathe.
